The Commission shall be comprised as follows:
One member from the Democratic Party Central Committee of Washington County;
One member from the Republican Party Central Committee of Washington County;
One member from the Washington County Chamber of Commerce;
One member from the Washington County Farm Bureau;
One member from the League of Women Voters of Washington County;
One member from the Western Maryland Central Labor Council;
One member from the Cumberland Valley Associated Builders and Contractors, Inc.;
One member from the Joint Veterans Council of Washington County; and
One member at large selected by the Washington County Retired Teachers Association.
